<item>
            <title>[HBASE-11330] Deprecate ThreadLocal and remove Reusable from PoolMap</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11330</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Reusable is not used anywhere and ThreadLocal is not recommend. See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11313&quot; title=&quot;RpcClient should allow Reusable pool option.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-11313&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-11313&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for other details.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So let&apos;s remove Reusable and deprecate ThreadLocal.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
