                            <comment id="14710872" author="ikeda" created="Tue, 25 Aug 2015 08:30:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;For RpcClientImpl, threads to put to PoolMap differ from threads to remove from it, and using ThreadLocal PoolMap always makes RpcClientImpl unstoppable, as far as I know. It is a complete bug to enable to use ThreadLocal PoolMap for RpcClientImpl.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
